title: US trade delegation heads to Beijing for talks
text:
US trade delegation heads to Beijing for talks Wednesday, May 02, 2018 - 01:34
As U.S. President Donald Trump's trade delegation prepares for negotiations in Beijing, Trump's chief trade negotiator said on Tuesday he was not looking to negotiate changes to China's state-driven economic system but would seek to expose it to more foreign competition.
